org.apache.felix.ipojo.extender.internal.processor

Class QueuingActivationProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.felix.ipojo.extender.internal.processor.ForwardingBundleProcessor
      • org.apache.felix.ipojo.extender.internal.processor.QueuingActivationProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BundleProcessor, Lifecycle

    public class QueuingActivationProcessor
extends ForwardingBundleProcessor
    A bundle processor submitting the activating job to the queue service. The submitted job relies on a delegated bundle processor.
